/* Type definitions for exporting and importing of models. */
/**
 * A map from Tensor dtype to number of bytes per element of the Tensor.
 */
export const DTYPE_VALUE_SIZE_MAP = {
  'float32': 4,
  'float16': 2,
  'int32': 4,
  'uint16': 2,
  'uint8': 1,
  'bool': 1,
  'complex64': 8
};
